          <li>Maintenance: Reduces the flatpak package size by cleaning up the blueprint compiler after building.</li>
          <li>Maintenance: Updates fava as well as other python package dependencies.</li>
        </ul>
      </description>
    </release>
    <release version="0.2.6" date="2023-08-27">
      <description>
        <p>Better desktop integration.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>New feature: This release improves the app's integration with the GNOME desktop. The Fava Desktop app is now associated with *.beancount files, allowing users to choose "Open with..." and to then choose "Fava" in GNOME Files.</li>
          <li>New feature: It is now possible to open beancount files in favagtk straight from GNOME Files (or any other file explorer, for that matter).</li>
          <li>Maintenance: Updates to GNOME 44, updates fava and beancount.</li>
          <li>Maintenance> Updates various dependencies including blueprint and python libraries.</li>
        </ul>
      </description>
    </release>
